shoes and see if you could hold steady for 2{ years,'' Mrs. Bakker
said.
   A sobbing Bakker was led away in handcuffs and manacles Thursday
after a psychiatrist reported that he had been hallucinating and
cowering in a fetal position in his lawyer's office.
