much of a fairly sluggish session. The industrial average rose 9.12
to 2,737.27, pushed up by a late round of buying.
   Advancing issues outnumbered declining ones by nearly 6 to 5 in
nationwide trading of New York Stock Exchange-listed stocks, with
801 up, 672 down and 510 unchanged.
   Volume on the floor of the Big Board eased to 143.42 million
